    <item>
      <title>法国加强对币安洗钱调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/french-step-up-money-laundering-investigation-into-binance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国检察官加强了对币安的洗钱调查，并指派一名拥有更强调查权力的调查法官来领导此案。]]></description>
